可以睇翻佢地出既post 全部都係講其他私校差 但對hkue就無咩評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係依個post就不停贊hkue<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打手們係咪太多負面野 驚學生search到要網上既毒針 開始開post洗正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 一定唔好讀任何一間私校 寧願讀ive(見過好多學生讀左一年或兩年 之後走翻去讀ive 個個都話浪費哂啲時間)"},{"pid":"86b42aa55c45f671b62ad1834ceeb71beea407d5","tid":273261,"uid":16248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:03:18.000Z","msg":"成班打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975ae6424c3ea29e758a45aa665e0d62d22ddb5c","tid":273261,"uid":120196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:04:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95c18acaddd99913b12f85826d5a2bbab3c9b564","tid":273261,"uid":97996,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:06:45.000Z","msg":"咁如果有認證都好似係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家啲人係鳩唔係都話人係打手嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc20f01505f6589695564159fba5138e31f4ecc","tid":273261,"uid":120049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:11:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b391bbf5b88f4ca7af7a94ad3f0564fca18f273","tid":273261,"uid":120161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:14:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0aa7ff2376291509ad5be0d2582c841e959233b6","tid":273261,"uid":4689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁如果有認證都好似係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家啲人係鳩唔係都話人係打手嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只係你唔知道佢地用左幾多錢係出面請打手 到左打call約學生既高峰期 就不停開正評post 仲要狂kick個網 希望啲dse學生想search到既都係正評post 順利full pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  班學生顧問(傳銷狗)啲佣金就袋袋平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f0128f7972aa4072d960c1d3225496348a8ab4","tid":273261,"uid":23727,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:15:25.000Z","msg":"成班打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔好讀 成間野好戇鳩 讀完出黎咪又係做酒店炒散 呀豬呀狗都炒得啦 入到去做長工都只會係鴨仔 咁到底讀黎有乜撚野用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申炒緊散 識好多舊同學都係炒緊散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac95dc3f22be253b3c33070debeb144b8f25ac19","tid":273261,"uid":120048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:16:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21256bcc3a9221ef55c354c6c9942d398510983b","tid":273261,"uid":4689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>hkue狗也不屌<br />\n話asso升u率得幾%嗰啲不如返去做下功課先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心問，asso升u率其實有幾多？<br />\n之前睇新聞話啲學院聲稱嘅數據其實都好有誤導性</blockquote><br />\n講真所謂既升u率只單單係講緊8大 連啲野雞大學既topup都計埋入去 升u率實就架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13db752df115a9eb0e8089d44251a9fcb7ab578d","tid":273261,"uid":4689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>hkue狗也不屌<br />\n話asso升u率得幾%嗰啲不如返去做下功課先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心問，asso升u率其實有幾多？<br />\n之前睇新聞話啲學院聲稱嘅數據其實都好有誤導性</blockquote><br />\n我都想知，係咪睇呢d<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/021632_a084d852cea65cfa3f7b263238ef69ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F021632_a084d852cea65cfa3f7b263238ef69ff.jpg&h=c950da8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/021638_56550c7bbc0edfde5914b93cbcf3935d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F021638_56550c7bbc0edfde5914b93cbcf3935d.jpg&h=fe797571&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nAsso係無用 但啲私校更加無用"},{"pid":"7343f56168b7476352080e4b316744cb0fdc4f67","tid":273261,"uid":120161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:20:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24aa34a11264f482ddb6b10e74738b09914b6a86","tid":273261,"uid":15704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我表弟當年都係讀呢間 ， 我有認真幫佢睇過，係澳洲政府個網都搵到呢個course註冊。<br />\n讀完degree 係香港都搵到政府工 。點都好過asso 搏果幾個%入local u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你有無同佢一齊讀呢間先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f52c26cd6e920a7f0b9d535933616fad9f764f2","tid":273261,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:21:46.000Z","msg":"去上過course 唔錯<br />\n但升學免喇"},{"pid":"7cba14077f426ea17b6133128c34a693c8ab7d33","tid":273261,"uid":120048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ae3fd935f59f626453ad493094a71f1c39aeb89","tid":273261,"uid":120147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:23:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cd56ae9b0d8f6f39a18a4cebc35c21e0aa8830c","tid":273261,"uid":23727,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:23:36.000Z","msg":"好老實講句，先唔講間野有啲乜乜乜認證，讀呢間野係要考個分班試嘅 ,屌你老母我見過最勁嗰兩班都有一堆人dse 係得個位數字，然後依家同你講話呢堆得個位數字嘅學生讀撚完呢個濕鳩program 之後出到黎會勁過係BU grad 嘅大學生，你信唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663a391d47245c89cbf3ee52c10e509f2099cb60","tid":273261,"uid":4689,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>hkue狗也不屌<br />\n話asso升u率得幾%嗰啲不如返去做下功課先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心問，asso升u率其實有幾多？<br />\n之前睇新聞話啲學院聲稱嘅數據其實都好有誤導性</blockquote><br />\n講真所謂既升u率只單單係講緊8大 連啲野雞大學既topup都計埋入去 升u率實就架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁讀野雞咪一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁真係入8大呢有幾多？<br />\n利申 4年前幫啊妹去太空聽talk佢話大約100人有5個入到</blockquote><br />\n讀埋啲野雞大學 出到嚟無認受性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不如讀hd好過"},{"pid":"9cf558692ae06fc7037ea630579ce3b5b2029b23","tid":273261,"uid":120147,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2303f1126dd2a5badcaf6c7345f99ee2843787d1","tid":273261,"uid":23727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成班打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔好讀 成間野好戇鳩 讀完出黎咪又係做酒店炒散 呀豬呀狗都炒得啦 入到去做長工都只會係鴨仔 咁到底讀黎有乜撚野用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申炒緊散 識好多舊同學都係炒緊散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾打手feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我師兄姐喺酒店做長工俾哂d辛苦野炒散做，但又識幾多蛇頭ga wo，介紹我地炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  炒得勁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  長工正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁唔通你啲師兄師姐會同你話講&quot;我係酒店到做得好慘好辛苦呀&quot;<br />\n長工正呀 緊係正啦 但AM 以上先正呀 入到去做鴨仔日日比大粒指撚住黎屌呀<br />\n識蛇頭有幾難 你長炒嘅話佢真頭想主動識你添啦 夠social 嘅話是旦炒番半年都已經一堆蛇頭一堆場比你揀"},{"pid":"e89edd067ed3f8a0803f76007e655769068e6cc2","tid":273261,"uid":51673,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:29:57.000Z","msg":"10年前讀完<br />\n升topup再讀master洗底<br />\n之後仲要讀cfa等等<br />\n讀書路好漫長<br />\n早知用同樣價錢不如去讀護士，幾年讀完又搵到錢<br />\n又有後宮生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d5d536f1160a068a0ca0438597d7c2ba93d113","tid":273261,"uid":41098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T20:13:08.000Z","msg":"上面班打手全部死全家"},{"pid":"336e4f6c0f015900565e07280836cde97267d6d4","tid":273261,"uid":90605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:07:15.000Z","msg":"香港環球教育集團(HKUE)<br />\n之前去過班Sell屎有佣分<br />\n條友喝一大支水<br />\n之後踏ive乜乜乜<br />\n又話我失業<br />\nhkue點點點<br />\n真係好落力"},{"pid":"3290f40bd9d6f42f7c65991e04c9e3ae2d453e5c","tid":273261,"uid":37874,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score"